S.FORM: Siliq qani ga qbhniq na Tayal uyi. maki calay yaw ga talam ta ssiliq qani. Ana ga cquliq s'ciq hiya ga nyan naha galan utux qbhniq qani. Siliq qani ga qbhniq na Tayal, sisin san naha kayal qa tyuku hiya, yaw siliq ga lmam ktayux yaw, talam silq san ta, skahul ta ryaniq 'san nya ki pinnhwaw nya cpung yaw nqu musa qmalup qani musa baqun qa gaga psaniq uyi, ita Tayal hiya ga s'agal ta tmalam yaw qa qbhniq qa siliq qani.
